      "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body": "I know the REST interface requires less tooling to consume than the RPC interface, but would be helpful to better understand exactly why the `gettxspendingprevout` RPC does not suffice here? Is the JSON (de)serialization overhead unacceptable? I.e. is a REST equivalent a necessity, or a nice to have?",
